name: NestedLineStyles
shortdesc: A collection of nested line styles.

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.shortdesc: Initial values for properties of the new NestedLineStyle

method.name: count
method.shortdesc: Displays the number of elements in the NestedLineStyle.

method.name: item
method.shortdesc: Returns the NestedLineStyle with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.shortdesc: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

method.name: itemByRange
method.shortdesc: Returns the NestedLineStyles within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.shortdesc: The NestedLineStyle, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: NestedLineStyle, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.shortdesc: The NestedLineStyle, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: NestedLineStyle, Long Integer or String.

method.name: firstItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the first NestedLineStyle in the collection.

method.name: lastItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the last NestedLineStyle in the collection.

method.name: middleItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the middle NestedLineStyle in the collection.

method.name: previousItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the NestedLineStyle with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The index of the NestedLineStyle that follows the desired NestedLineStyle.

method.name: nextItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the NestedLineStyle whose index follows the specified NestedLineStyle in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The NestedLineStyle whose index comes before the desired NestedLineStyle.

method.name: anyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns any NestedLineStyle in the collection.

method.name: everyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns every NestedLineStyle in the collection.

method.name: toSource
method.shortdesc: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the NestedLineStyle.
Returns the NestedLineStyle with the specified index.

property.name: length
property.shortdesc: The number of objects in the collection.
